title: Michael Sieben's Internet Shack - Season 2 Episode 2
description:
Check out Season 2, Episode #2 of Michael Sieben's Internet Shack where Sieben and Denver 
discover a magical ditch. Holy stokes!!! Sometimes it takes a serious head injury and a talk 
with God to realize what matters the most in this world. Money. Duh
